      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This example remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting meticulous ownership and an uncompromising standard of maintenance. From its flawless exterior finish to its untouched interior appointments, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. An ideal acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
