      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Clean title. Inspection ready.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule, this vehicle is offered in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior boasts its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The body lines are laser-straight, and all glass and trim remain crystal clear. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather seating is supple and entirely free of bolster wear or creasing, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every dashboard component, electronic interface, and switch operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to concours standards, reflecting a rigorous, documented maintenance history performed exclusively by certified specialists. The car drives with the tightness and silence of the day it left the assembly line, sitting on a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is a rare, investment-grade example suited for the most demanding collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
