    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 996.2 Carrera 4S, featuring the 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus and a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This wide-body example exhibits zero bore scoring and has received a proactive IMS bearing retrofit with a dual-row ceramic solution. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by factory-spec Bilstein dampers and Turbo-derived four-piston monoblock calipers. All-wheel-drive viscous coupling remains within strict operating parameters, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen with an immaculate undercarriage and flawless paint depth.",
